idden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tgz1665702585851.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tgz1665702585851.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tgz1665702585851.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tgz1665702585851\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Inherits From\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__section_w1094ab1b5b1_w1095ab1b5_w1096ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__table_d10898e1_d10899e1_d10900e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Technical Name:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n                                 TEMPLATENAME\n                                </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Expected Value:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Name of the modeled object from which this derived object inherits.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default Value:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__section_ivg_1yj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d519993e94\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__p_d97277e1_d97278e1_d97279e1\">Derived objects can inherit from modeled objects, and\n            subtype entities and fields can inherit from the their supertypes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__p_d97280e1_d97281e1_d97282e1\">If the property <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherits</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, the object is derived, and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Inherits\n               From</span> property specifies the URI of the modeled object.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__section_gfh_byj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d519993e115\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__ul_fc1_dyj_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39521e1_d39522e1_d39523e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39524e1_d39525e1_d39526e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39527e1_d39528e1_d39529e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39530e1_d39531e1_d39532e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39533e1_d39534e1_d39535e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnq1665702702174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnq1665702702174.html\" title=\"A Subtype Entity specializes a Modeled Entity (also known as the Supertype Entity). It is used to define a data set (or subset) for a special purpose, but that can be stored in the same database table as its Supertype.\">Subtype Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgz1665702585851__li_d39536e1_d39537e1_d39538e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kgf1665703025767.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kgf1665703025767.html\" title=\"A Subtype Field references a Supertype Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\">Subtype Field</a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtg1665702585772.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Inherits</a><p>This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616079\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616079\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Inherits From Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Inherits From This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable. Technical Name: TEMPLATENAME Expected Value: Name of the modeled object from which this derived object inherits. Default Value: None Description Derived objects can inherit from modeled objects, and subtype entities and fields can inherit from the their supertypes. If the property Inherits is True , the object is derived, and the Inherits From property specifies the URI of the modeled object. Applies To Component Component Entity Component Field Label Subtype Entity Subtype Field Related Links Inherits This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}